Arsenal are in talks over extending their pre-season tour of Asia later this year.

The Gunners will head to Singapore in the summer to take part in the Barclays Asia Trophy, together with Everton, Stoke and a Singapore Select XI.

The tournament will run from July 15-18, but there are plans in place to play an extra match in Thailand a few days later.

